パッケージ ch.uzh.ifi.seal.changedistiller.model.entities

クラス SourceCodeEntity

java.lang.Object
ch.uzh.ifi.seal.changedistiller.model.entities.SourceCodeEntity
public class SourceCodeEntity
extends java.lang.Object
Source code entity representing one particular AST node.

Each source code entity has a EntityType describing the type of the source code entity. The unique name of a source code entity depends on its EntityType.

作成者:
Beat Fluri, Giacomo Ghezzi, zubi, Michael Wuersch
